name: Pitik Jago
description:
Pitik Jago is one of Indonesia's heritage that symbolized resurgence.  A necessity spirit in the midst of this chaos and mad crisis. Say it health and environment and many else unsaid. Especially on this independence day.

All in all were put together in this very picture. A Pitik Jago, standing straight on a puddle of human trash.

Shot on Canon EOS 5/Agfa 200 | C41 Process | Fuji Frontier Scan | 3602 × 2397px
